      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it\u2019s honestly in pristine, like-new condition. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person\u2014not a single flaw to be found! If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been loved and kept in perfect shape, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
