    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-level example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The double-VANOS variable valve timing has been meticulously serviced, ensuring optimal cam phasing across the rev range. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains factory-stiff with documented subframe reinforcement, riding on a perfectly damped suspension with bushings in peak kinetic condition. Finished in original paint with zero oxidation, the interior preserves the factory tactile feel of the Nappa leather and switchgear. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero mechanical deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
