    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-floor state, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its initial delivery. The exterior paintwork retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, completely free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no signs of wear or bolster compression, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every mechanical component has been serviced strictly according to manufacturer intervals, with a comprehensive folder of documentation included. From the pristine alloy wheels to the untouched undercarriage, this car is for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection. It drives as tight and responsive as the day it rolled off the assembly line. Truly a rare find for those seeking the absolute best of its kind.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, an offering that defines the standard for the pre-owned market. This specimen remains in pristine condition, showcasing a flawless aesthetic and mechanical integrity that mirrors its original factory delivery. Every surface, from the hand-selected interior materials to the lustrous exterior finish, has been maintained with rigorous attention to detail. This is a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector or driver to acquire a vehicle of uncompromising caliber.",
      "price": 48950.0,
