    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and there isn't a single scratch or blemish to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for your next big adventure. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a peek for yourself!",
      "price": 44500.0,
