      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen exhibits exceptional mechanical integrity, with a recently serviced subframe and rod bearings addressed for longevity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Suspension geometry remains true, maintaining the chassis's renowned lateral rigidity and communicative steering rack. Finished in a concours-level exterior with zero oxidation or clear coat failure, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
